#: frontend/src/metabase/admin/permissions/constants/data-permissions.tsx:20
msgid "No self-service (Deprecated)"
msgstr "Без self-service (Deprecated)"

#: frontend/src/metabase/admin/permissions/components/DataPermissionsHelp/DataPermissionsHelp.tsx:78
msgid "The group can't use the query builder or drill through existing questions. They also can't see the data in the Browse data section. They can still view questions based on this data, if they have permissions to the relevant collection. ‘Blocked‘, ‘Impersonated‘ and ‘Row and column security‘ in another group will override ‘No self-service‘."
msgstr "Групата не може да използва конструктора на заявки или да прави drill-through през съществуващи въпроси. Също така не може да вижда данните в секцията Преглед на данни. Все пак може да преглежда въпроси, базирани на тези данни, ако има права за съответната колекция. „Blocked“, „Impersonated“ и „Row and column security“ в друга група ще заместят „No self-service“."

#: frontend/src/metabase/admin/permissions/components/DataPermissionsHelp/DataPermissionsHelp.tsx:84
#: frontend/src/metabase/admin/permissions/components/DataPermissionsHelp/DataPermissionsHelp.tsx:121
